Gosub INIT_IBAN From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BICCOD From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_CUR From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_TYPPAY From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_PAYPCT From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_CPYBAN From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BNF From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_MODSTL From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_MIDPAB1 From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_MIDPAB2 From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_MIDCRY From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_ACCNONREI From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_EXPNUM From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BANACCTYP From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BANBRCNUM From WMC1EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
