Gosub INIT_UPDDATTIM From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_AUUID From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_AGNID From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BANACCTYP1 From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BSOROL From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_PAYSPT From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BACREF From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BNKDEF From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BNKACCNUM From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_BNKSRTCOD From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_PAYAMT From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_IBAN2 From WMC2EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub AINIT From WMC0EMPLORIB : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
If this.snapshotEnabled=1 & this.APARENT=null
 [L]ASTASNAPSHOT = this.freeSnapshot
Endif
Return

####################################################################
# _ALOADATTRIBUTE
